{{define "content"}}
<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Science Newsletter</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        A monthly digest of recent academic papers tailored to your research interests.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
        The service syncs your researcher profile from
        <a href="https://openalex.org" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">OpenAlex</a>,
        tracks papers from authors you frequently cite, and uses AI to filter and summarize
        the most relevant new work. You get one email on the 1st of each month.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
        This is a small community service, not a commercial product. If you'd like access,
        ask the person who told you about it.
    </p>
</div>
{{end}}
